OL,7,FThe families of the victims of Valdo
OL,8,FCalocane have said services caring for
OL,9,Fhim in the lead-up to the attacks
OL,10,F"have blood on their hands", after it
OL,11,Femerged a mental health trust
OL,12,F"minimised or omitted" key details of
OL,13,Fthe serious risk he posed to others.
