OL,7,FThe final part of a Care Quality
OL,8,FCommission (CQC) review into the care
OL,9,Fof Calocane by Nottinghamshire
OL,10,FHealthcare NHS Foundation Trust (NHFT)
OL,11,Ffound risk assessments played down the
OL,12,Ffact he was refusing to take his
OL,13,Fmedication and was having ongoing and
OL,14,Fpersistent symptoms of psychosis.
OL,16,FIt also questions how well the trust
OL,17,Fengaged with Calocane's family, who
OL,18,Fraised concerns about his mental state.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/19
