OL,5,Comitted'
OL,7,FThe victims' families said the CQC
OL,8,Freport "demonstrates gross, systematic
OL,9,Ffailures" and also claim they have had
OL,10,Fconfirmation that a public inquiry
OL,11,Finto the case will take place.
OL,13,FCalocane stabbed students Barnaby
OL,14,FWebber and Grace O'Malley-Kumar, both
OL,15,F19, as they returned from a night out
OL,16,Fin the early hours of June 13 last
OL,17,Fyear, before killing Ian Coates, 65.
