OL,7,FThe special review of mental health
OL,8,Fservices at NHFT was ordered by then
OL,9,Fhealth secretary Victoria Atkins in
OL,10,FJanuary after Calocane was sentenced
OL,11,Fto an indefinite hospital order.
OL,13,FThe CQC said Calocane's records make
OL,14,Fit "clear" that he was "acutely
OL,15,Funwell" throughout the two years he
OL,16,Fwas under the care of NHFT.
OL,18,FHe was psychotic and suffering from
OL,19,Fparanoid delusions before eventually
OL,20,Fbeing diagnosed with paranoid
OL,21,Fschizophrenia in July 2020.
