OL,7,FBetween May 2020 and February 2022,
OL,8,Feight risk assessments were completed
OL,9,Ffor Calocane by the trust, which the
OL,10,FCQC said appear to have been carried
OL,11,Fout for each of his admissions to
OL,12,Fhospital and updated at other times
OL,13,Fduring his care.
OL,15,FThe regulator said that while some
OL,16,Frisks were highlighted, other
OL,17,Fassessments "minimised or omitted key
OL,18,Fdetails".
OL,26,@yD@MOUzD@HO]
