OL,7,FThese include the fact Calocane
OL,8,Frefused to take his medication, had
OL,9,Fongoing and persistent symptoms of
OL,10,Fpsychosis, was violent to others when
OL,11,Fpsychosis was not managed well, and
OL,12,Fescalated his violent behaviour in the
OL,13,Flater stages of his care.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/19
