OL,7,F"While it is not possible to say that
OL,8,Fthe devastating events of June 13 2023
OL,9,Fwould not have taken place had Valdo
OL,10,FCalocane received that support, what
OL,11,Fis clear is that the risk he presented
OL,12,Fto the public was not managed well and
OL,13,Fthat opportunities to mitigate that
OL,14,Frisk were missed."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@RO]
