OL,7,FInstead, he was treated under section
OL,8,F2 of the act, which is usually for
OL,9,Fpatients who are not known to mental
OL,10,Fhealth services.
OL,12,FA statement from the families of
OL,13,FBarnaby Webber, Grace O'Malley-Kumar
OL,14,Fand Ian Coates, said: "This report
OL,15,Fdemonstrates gross, systematic
OL,16,Ffailures in the mental health trust in
OL,17,Ftheir dealings with Calocane, from
OL,18,Fbeginning to end.
OL,26,@vD@WOU
