OL,7,F"Clinicians involved at every stage of
OL,8,FCalocane's care must bear a heavy
OL,9,Fburden of responsibility for their
OL,10,Ffailures and poor decision-making.
OL,12,F"Sadly, this is the first of what we
OL,13,Fexpect to be a series of damning
OL,14,Freports concerning failures by public
OL,15,Fbodies in the lead up to the killings
OL,16,Fof our loved ones, and beyond.
OL,18,F"We were failed by multiple
OL,19,Forganisations pre and post June 13
OL,20,F2023."
