OL,7,FAmong its recommendations, the CQC
OL,8,Fsaid NHFT should review treatment
OL,9,Fplans for people with schizophrenia
OL,10,Fregularly, as well as ensuring
OL,11,Fclinical supervision of decisions to
OL,12,Fdetain people under section 2 and 3 of
OL,13,Fthe Mental Health Act.
OL,15,FIt also called for NHS England to
OL,16,Fpublish guidance setting out national
OL,17,Fstandards for care for people with
OL,18,Fcomplex psychosis and paranoid
OL,19,Fschizophrenia in the next 12 months.
