OL,7,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting, said:
OL,8,F"I want to assure myself and the
OL,9,Fcountry that the failures identified
OL,10,Fin Nottinghamshire are not being
OL,11,Frepeated elsewhere.
OL,13,F"I expect the findings and
OL,14,Frecommendations in this report to be
OL,15,Fconsidered and applied throughout the
OL,16,Fcountry so that other families do not
OL,17,Fexperience the unimaginable pain that
OL,18,FBarnaby, Grace and Ian's family are
OL,19,Fliving with."
