OL,7,FThe handling of the Calocane case
OL,8,Fprompted outcry and led to numerous
OL,9,Finquiries into the public bodies
OL,10,Finvolved, including Nottinghamshire
OL,11,FPolice and Leicestershire Police.
OL,13,FThe victims' families added: "Along
OL,14,Fwith the Leicestershire and
OL,15,FNottinghamshire police forces, these
OL,16,Fdepartments and individual
OL,17,Fprofessionals have blood on their
OL,18,Fhands.
OL,26,@uD@^OU
